Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.83,0:22:58.51,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}The world is too slow to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.51,0:23:00.59,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}Not all blossoms spark
